    <title>网页基础</title>
    <link href="https://li-san-huo.gitee.io/2023/08/10/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/"/>
    <id>https://li-san-huo.gitee.io/2023/08/10/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</id>
    <published>2023-08-10T07:04:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-08-10T12:10:19.645Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="html基本语法"><a href="#html基本语法" class="headerlink" title="html基本语法"></a>html基本语法</h1><h1 id="VScode的使用"><a href="#VScode的使用" class="headerlink" title="VScode的使用"></a>VScode的使用</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">网页开发工具有很多，比如记事本、DW、sublime、webStorm、Hbuiler、vscode等</span><br><span class="line">主流使用的是VScode,使用详细介绍：</span><br><span class="line">1.在桌面上新建一个根目录（文件夹），在vscode中打开</span><br><span class="line">2.安装插件</span><br><span class="line">3.新建文件及文件夹</span><br><span class="line">4.快速生成网页的基本结构！回车</span><br><span class="line">5.自动保存文件-自动保存</span><br><span class="line">6.打开浏览器Alt+b</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">快捷键：</span><br><span class="line">ctrl+c复制+v粘贴+s保存+z撤销+y恢复</span><br><span class="line">其他浏览器打开：shift+alt+b</span><br><span class="line">侧边栏的显示隐藏：Ctrl+b</span><br><span class="line">代码格式化：Shift+Alt+F</span><br><span class="line">放大缩小视图ctrl +加号/减号</span><br><span class="line">向下复制一行：Shift+Alt+Down</span><br><span class="line">在当前行下方插入一行：Ctrl+Enter</span><br><span class="line">多行编辑：Alt+Shift+鼠标左键</span><br><span class="line">下一个匹配的也被选中：Ctrl+D</span><br><span class="line">折叠Ctrl+Shift+[ 展开 Ctrl+Shift+]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><hr><h1 id="photoshop的基本操作"><a href="#photoshop的基本操作" class="headerlink" title="photoshop的基本操作"></a>photoshop的基本操作</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">打开： Ctrl+o、将文件拖入PS</span><br><span class="line">新建：Ctrl+ N</span><br><span class="line">存储：选择存储文件格式、名字、位置。</span><br><span class="line">移动工具：可以移动图层、参考线等</span><br><span class="line">标尺：ctrl+R</span><br><span class="line">参考线：按住标尺拖拽</span><br><span class="line">取色：取色工具、前景色和背景色</span><br><span class="line">矩形选框量尺寸、取消选区 ctrl+D</span><br><span class="line">放大镜：Alt+ 鼠标滚轮</span><br><span class="line">抓手工具：空格</span><br><span class="line">撤销：Ctrl+Z（一步）、Ctrl+alt+z（多步）</span><br><span class="line">自由变换：ctrl+T</span><br><span class="line">切片工具的使用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="网页"><a href="#网页" class="headerlink" title="网页"></a>网页</h1><p>是构成网站的基本元素，它通常由图片、链接、文字、声音、视频等元素组成。index.html</p><hr><h1 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML:"></a>HTML:</h1><ul><li><p><strong>超文本标记语言（Hyper Text Matkup Language），用来描述网页的一种语言。</strong></p></li><li><p>不是一种编辑语言，而是一种标记语言（markup language）</p></li></ul><hr><h1 id="网页的形成："><a href="#网页的形成：" class="headerlink" title="网页的形成："></a>网页的形成：</h1><ul><li>前端人员开发代码—–&gt; 浏览器显示代码（解析、渲染）—–&gt; 生成最后的Web页面</li></ul><hr><h1 id="常用浏览器："><a href="#常用浏览器：" class="headerlink" title="常用浏览器："></a>常用浏览器：</h1><ul><li>作用：是网页显示、运行的平台。</li><li><strong>五大浏览器：IE、火狐(Firefox)、谷歌(Google)、苹果(Safari)和欧朋(Opera)。</strong></li><li>浏览器内核：负责读取网页内容，整理讯息，计算网页的显示方式并显示页面。</li><li>chrome的内核Blink</li></ul><hr><h1 id="web标准："><a href="#web标准：" class="headerlink" title="web标准："></a><strong>web标准：</strong></h1><p><strong>是由W3C组织和其他标准化组织制定的一系列标准的集合。</strong></p><ol><li><strong>结构:html</strong></li><li><strong>样式:css</strong></li><li><strong>行为:js</strong></li></ol><hr><h1 id="html语法"><a href="#html语法" class="headerlink" title="html语法"></a>html语法</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1、HTML 标签是由尖括号包围的关键词，例如<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span>。</span><br><span class="line">2、标签的分类：</span><br><span class="line">    双标签：大部分标签是成对出现的，p h1。</span><br><span class="line">    单表签：极少情况是单个标签，列如br,img,也称为空元素。</span><br><span class="line">3、特点：</span><br><span class="line">    HTML标记不区分大小写，建议使用小写</span><br><span class="line">    所有标签都是放在<span class="tag">&lt;&gt;</span>里</span><br><span class="line">    标签关系分为：包含关系和并列关系</span><br><span class="line">    标签可以互相合理嵌套</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="基本结构"><a href="#基本结构" class="headerlink" title="基本结构"></a>基本结构</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>网页标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1.<span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE&gt;</span>声明文档类型，位于html标签的前面，告诉浏览器按照html5规范解析页面</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2.<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span>用来定义当前文档显示的语言。en 英文，zh-CN 中文</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">3.<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 声明字符编码方式，防止乱码</span><br><span class="line">    规定 HTML </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;html基本语法&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#html基本语法&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;html基本语法&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;html基本语法&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 id=&quot;VScode的使用&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#VScode的使用&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;VScode的使用&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;VScode的使用&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight html&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;网页开发工具有很多，比如记事本、DW、sublime、webStorm、Hbuiler、vscode等&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;主流使用的是VScode,使用详细介绍：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1.在桌面上新建一个根目录（文件夹），在vscode中打开&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2.安装插件&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3.新建文件及文件夹&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4.快速生成网页的基本结构！回车&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5.自动保存	文件-自动保存&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6.打开浏览器Alt+b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;快捷键：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ctrl+c复制	+v粘贴	+s保存	+z撤销	+y恢复&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;其他浏览器打开：shift+alt+b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;侧边栏的显示隐藏：Ctrl+b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;代码格式化：	Shift+Alt+F&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;放大缩小视图	ctrl +加号/减号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;向下复制一行：	Shift+Alt+Down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;在当前行下方插入一行：	Ctrl+Enter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;多行编辑：	Alt+Shift+鼠标左键&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;下一个匹配的也被选中：	Ctrl+D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;折叠	Ctrl+Shift+[ 展开 Ctrl+Shift+]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
